    "laboratory_requirements": {
      "description": "No laboratory tests, bloodwork, or paramedical exam requirements are specified—SimpliNow underwriting is fully simplified issue, relying solely on the height/weight build chart and the medical questionnaire (Conditions page 4–7).",
